Package: requirements
Type: Package
Title: Version Specific Project Library Management
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Mark", "Ewing", email="b.mark@ewingsonline.com", role=c("aut","cre")),
  person("Adam", "Spannbauer", role=c("aut"))
  )
BugReports: https://github.com/bmewing/requirements/issues
Description: Brings support to R for Python style requirements management via the requirements.txt file.
  Will eventually support most of the PEP 440 standard as described https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0440/#version-specifiers.
  Enables easy documentation of packages used along with single line installation and single line package loading in R.
